OL,3,CFather who murdered baby daughter by
OL,4,Cshaking her has sentence increased
OL,6,FA father from Kent who was jailed for
OL,7,Fmurdering his baby daughter by shaking
OL,8,Fher so hard she suffered brain
OL,9,Finjuries has had his sentence
OL,10,Fincreased at the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FThomas Holford was jailed for life
OL,13,Fwith a minimum term of 16 years at
OL,14,FCanterbury Crown Court in July after
OL,15,Fbeing convicted of killing his
OL,16,Fdaughter, Everleigh Stroud.
