OL,3,CFather who murdered baby daughter by
OL,4,Cshaking her has sentence increased
OL,6,FEverleigh had been left alone in her
OL,7,Ffather's care on the night of Tuesday
OL,8,F20 April 2021, when she was just five
OL,9,Fweeks old, and was left with brain and
OL,10,Fbone injuries after being shaken with
OL,11,F'excessive and severe' force by
OL,12,FHolford at her grandparents' home in
OL,13,FRamsgate, Kent.
OL,15,FShe spent more than a year in hospital
OL,16,Fbefore dying aged 14 months on Friday
OL,17,F27 May 2022.
