OL,3,CFather who murdered baby daughter by
OL,4,Cshaking her has sentence increased
OL,6,FThe Solicitor General, Ellie Reeves,
OL,7,Freferred Holford's sentence to the
OL,8,FCourt of Appeal in September as
OL,9,F'unduly lenient'.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, barristers told a hearing
OL,12,Fthat aggravating features in the case
OL,13,F'significantly outweighed the
OL,14,Favailable mitigation', including that
OL,15,FHolford was "heavily intoxicated with
OL,16,Fcannabis" at the time of the fatal
OL,17,Fattack on Everleigh.
OL,19,FIn a ruling, three senior judges
OL,20,Fagreed and increased the minimum term
OL,21,Fof Holford's sentence by two years.
