OL,6,FLord Justice Edis, sitting with Mr
OL,7,FJustice Sheldon and Mr Justice Calver,
OL,8,Fsaid: "He was aware that if he took
OL,9,Fsubstantial quantities of cannabis,
OL,10,Fhis ability to control himself may
OL,11,Fsuffer.
OL,13,F"He nevertheless deliberately did
OL,14,Fthat, knowing that in the night to
OL,15,Fcome, he was to be the sole carer for
OL,16,Fhis five-week-old daughter."
