OL,6,FHe continued: "As matters turned out,
OL,7,Fhe was therefore taking risks with her
OL,8,Flife that he had no right to take.
OL,9,FThat is a significant aggravating
OL,10,Ffactor."
OL,12,FJocelyn Ledward KC, for the Solicitor
OL,13,FGeneral, said in written submissions
OL,14,Fthat Holford, who is now 25 and was 20
OL,15,Fat the time he attacked Everleigh, had
OL,16,Fbeen a regular cannabis user.
