OL,6,FHe had been seen handling his daughter
OL,7,F'gently and confidently' in the first
OL,8,Fweeks of her life, and had previously
OL,9,Fcared for her alone overnight without
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FOn the night of Tuesday 20 April 2021,
OL,13,FEverleigh's mother was visiting
OL,14,Ffriends, leaving her in Holford's sole
OL,15,Fcare.
OL,17,FHe said in text messages that he would
OL,18,Ffind looking after Everleigh
OL,19,F'stressful' and smoked cannabis on the
OL,20,Fnight she was attacked.
