OL,6,FMs Ledward told the court that
OL,7,FHolford's lack of previous convictions
OL,8,Fand previous good care for his
OL,9,Fdaughter was 'tempered' by his
OL,10,F'voluntary and excessive' use of
OL,11,Fcannabis.
OL,13,FShe said: "In the result, the minimum
OL,14,Fterm imposed was not just lenient, but
OL,15,Foutside the range that was available
OL,16,Fto the learned judge in this case, and
OL,17,Fthus unduly lenient."
OL,19,FJoanna Martin KC, for Holford, said in
OL,20,Fcourt: "My Lords will be unsurprised
OL,21,Fwhen I say the judge got it right.
