OL,6,F"While it may be a lenient sentence,
OL,7,Fit is not an unduly lenient sentence."
OL,9,FIncreasing Holford's minimum term,
OL,10,FLord Justice Edis said Everleigh was
OL,11,F'as vulnerable as any human person
OL,12,Fcould be' and that Holford had injured
OL,13,Fher 'grievously'.
OL,15,FHe said: "Everleigh's mother bitterly
OL,16,Fregrets her decision to leave the
OL,17,Fchild in the offender's care that
OL,18,Fnight and blames herself for what
OL,19,Fhappened.
