OL,6,FHolford watched proceedings remotely
OL,7,Ffrom HMP Long Lartin in Worcestershire
OL,8,Fand showed no emotion as his sentence
OL,9,Fwas increased.
OL,11,FSolicitor General Ellie Reeves said:
OL,12,F"This is a horrific and upsetting
OL,13,Fcase. Thomas Holford was meant to be
OL,14,Fcaring for his daughter, who was only
OL,15,Ffive weeks old, but instead he
OL,16,Fconsumed excessive amounts of drugs
OL,17,Fbefore violently attacking her.
