OL,6,F"Everleigh must have suffered
OL,7,Fimmensely, and those severe injuries
OL,8,Feventually led to her untimely death a
OL,9,Fyear later.
OL,11,F"Everleigh had her whole life ahead of
OL,12,Fher and there are no words that will
OL,13,Fbring comfort to those who loved and
OL,14,Fcherished her.
OL,16,F"I wish to offer my deepest sympathies
OL,17,Fand welcome the court's decision to
OL,18,Fkeep this dangerous man in prison for
OL,19,Flonger following his harrowing crimes."
